Smart Business Manager Pro
A modern desktop business management application built with Python and Tkinter.
Smart Business Manager Pro helps users track sales, expenses, profit, reports, and business performance through a clean dashboard interface with multi-page navigation.


Overview
Smart Business Manager Pro is designed to simplify small business record keeping.
The application allows users to:
	•	Record sales transactions
	•	Track expenses
	•	Monitor business profit
	•	Generate reports
	•	Export records
	•	Manage application settings
	•	View business summaries in a dashboard
The project combines functionality with a modern user interface.


Features
Dashboard
	•	Live business overview
	•	Total Sales
	•	Total Expenses
	•	Net Profit
	•	Transaction history
	•	Live clock

Sales Management
Users can:
	•	Enter Product Name
	•	Enter Quantity
	•	Enter Unit Price
	•	Automatically calculate totals
	•	Save transactions
	•	View sales 
Example:
Product: Rice
Quantity: 5
Unit Price: Le 100

Total: Le 500

Expense Management
Track business expenses with:
	•	Expense Name
	•	Category selection
	•	Quantity
	•	Unit Cost
	•	Notes section
	•	Automatic expense calculation

Categories include:
	•	Transport
	•	Utilities
	•	Salary
	•	Food
	•	Inventory
	•	Other

Example:
Expense: Fuel
Category: Transport
Quantity: 3
Unit Cost: Le 50
Total: Le 150


Reports
Generate business reports containing:
	•	Total Sales
	•	Total Expenses
	•	Profit/Loss
	•	Business status
	•	Recent transaction records

Export reports to:
“business_report.txt”


Settings
Application settings include:
	•	Dark Mode
	•	Reset Totals
	•	Clear Transaction History
	•	Export Report
	•	Business Status Indicator
	•	App Information

Profit Formula:
“Profit = Total Sales − Total Expenses”

Built With:
	•	Python 3
	•	Tkinter
	•	Datetime Module


